A simple app to decide what to cook for Breakfast.
It will show a Breakfast randomly. If you want to change it, simply Shake the phone!! 
Hope to make it the be all and end all cooking app for Indians!!

This app uses Android-MVC library to separate out the Data & the UI part: https://github.com/gauthamns/android-mvc
Be sure to download and include the library while testing this app.

App also uses prepopulated database to show a few common items.
